<taxonomicName id="E46BC02EF1AF2D108A0BEF99887CCD47" authorityName="Ward &amp; Boudinot" authorityYear="2021" baseAuthorityName="Ward &amp; Boudinot" baseAuthorityYear="2021" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Camponotus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Camponotus (Colobopsis) leucodiscus" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="leucodiscus" status="stat. rev." subGenus="Colobopsis">Camponotus (Colobopsis) leucodiscus</taxonomicName>
Wheeler, 1919: 117. Holotype dealate queen (by monotypy), British North Borneo (E. B. Kershaw) (MCZC) [examined via image on MCZbase: MCZ-ENT00021564]
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B8E329A4182186CD6166E0D4328B0223" pageId="0" pageNumber="37">
<taxonomicName id="4E4BCCA327B05BE520D9DEF8D6FAB857" authorityName="Ward &amp; Boudinot" authorityYear="2021" baseAuthorityName="Ward &amp; Boudinot" baseAuthorityYear="2021" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Camponotus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Camponotus (Colobopsis) leucodiscus" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="37" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="leucodiscus" status="stat. rev." subGenus="Colobopsis">Camponotus (Colobopsis) leucodiscus</taxonomicName>
